Class ReadFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • Logic.ReadFile

  • public class ReadFile
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a class that uses BufferedReader that let's you open a file you choose, read multiple Integers from a document read multiple lines from a document into a String array Search for a specific word in all caps in a document
